text: to wrap this up well thanks for joining
us at the first ever Cuban artists forum
in Delhi I would really love for all of
you to continue supporting the local
meetups here and make sure you attend
the meetups send speakers send
participants and you know sponsor some
food and drinks or anything like that in
the local meetups that will be really
useful this is the first event in Delhi
so I want you all to you know continue
your journey in Cuba notice and explore
what we have to offer here if you liked
what we have done here please join us in
other events that are happening for
example we have one in Amsterdam March
30th then we have Shanghai the CFP is
open until February 28th and
sponsorships are available too and there
were last stop this year is in my
hometown in Boston so please consider
coming there as well so if folks are
interested you know especially students
are interested then we do have travel
support program diversity scholarships
and things like that so please make use
of the opportunities that are available
and if you have any questions just hit
us up on in there again and for this
specific event the sponsorships are open
as well so thanks a lot and hope to see
you at the next event thank you
[Applause]
